title: Salt-n-pepa.Do You Want Me 92-VINYLRIP
description:
Salt -N- Pepa "Do You Want Me Baby"  1992 Remix by Ben Liebrand.

This remix features the riff from the "Peanuts" cartoon (Charlie Brown).

Couldn't find it digitally anywhere, so ripped the vinyl.

Ripped with the following:
ProTools 10 w/Digi002 Rack 
Technics 1200 w/ Stanton 680MP cartridge.

Recorded as AIFF with the following settings:
96khz @ 24-bit.
